   WITH
</P>
<P>
   KOSOVO FUTURE -- Although the political future of Kosovo is left
vague in the settlement that ended the war, American and NATO
officials say they envision an international protectorate that will
in theory be part of Yugoslavia but that may well, after a few
years, become independent. (Perlez, N.Y. Times News Service) Art
includes 2-column color photo of worried Albanian refugee.
