   GUNS-DEMOCRATS _ WASHINGTON _ With new gun controls headed for a
House floor vote as early as this week, as many as 30 Democrats
from conservative districts remain firmly opposed to new controls.
Several of them, particularly from Texas, receive substantial
financial support from the NRA. (Moscoso, Cox News Service). MOVED
Tuesday.
