<TEXT>
<P>
   The video column that moved this week from Cox News Service
contained errors in references to Alfred Hitchcock's ``Psycho'' and
``The Birds.'' Hitchcock is seen briefly in ``Psycho'' near Janet
Leigh's office. In ``The Birds,'' it is Tippi Hedren who walks into
the pet store near the beginning of the film, and it is Hedren
later smoking a cigarette as crows gather.
</P>
