<DOCNO> NYT19990612.0261 </DOCNO>
<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1999-06-12 23:31 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A3335 &Cx1f; taf-z
